dcat-distribution-strings.description:
Link to Catchment scale land use of Australia – Update December 2020 raster package (GeoTIFF and supporting files) – Zip [126 MB]. This zip file includes:

CLUM raster dataset of Catchment scale land use of Australia. GeoTIFF, 16 bit integer, resolution 50 metres by 50 metres, coordinate system GDA94 / Australian Albers.

Raster data assigned with 18 class, primary and secondary classes as depicted in the Australian Land Use and Management Classification (ALUMC) version 8, agricultural industries, date of mapping and scale of mapping.
dcat-distribution-strings.title: Raster package – GeoTIFF
